### Liste des services
GET http://localhost:3000/services

### Créer un service HTTP
POST http://localhost:3000/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "GitHub",
  "type": "HTTP",
  "target": "https://github.com",
  "intervalSeconds": 60
}

### Créer un service avec tous les champs
POST http://localhost:3000/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mon serveur Minecraft",
  "type": "TCP",
  "target": "localhost:25565",
  "intervalSeconds": 30,
  "timeoutMs": 3000,
  "failureThreshold": 5,
  "enabled": true
}